sections.heading: 01|Recycling, waste reduction, litter prevention definitions
sections.text: Effective:September 30, 2021Latest Legislation:House Bill 110 - 134th General AssemblyPDF:Download Authenticated PDFAs used in this chapter:(A) "Litter" means garbage, trash, waste, rubbish, ashes, cans, bottles, wire, paper, cartons, boxe
